    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Notice</strong>: Local multiplayer only. Online play is supported through <strong><i>Steam Remote Play Together</i></strong> and <strong><i>Parsec</i></strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815290/extras/c6fc732d41d0e06ee8721aebf95c6359.poster.avif?t=1755349297\" width=614 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815290/extras/c6fc732d41d0e06ee8721aebf95c6359.webm?t=1755349297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815290/extras/c6fc732d41d0e06ee8721aebf95c6359.mp4?t=1755349297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the ultimate hitmen party - a <strong><i>fast-paced</i></strong> and <strong><i>hilarious local multiplayer</i></strong> game for up to <strong>8 players</strong>. Blend in, hunt down the target and outsmart your friends in the race to become the best hitman.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of multiple game modes: from the classic <strong><i>Hitman</i></strong> mode to the unique challenges of <strong><i>Dress-up</i></strong> and <strong><i>Bodyguard</i></strong>, there's always a new way to beat your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Get creative</i></strong> and <strong><i>stay incognito</i></strong> in Hitmen Party's interactive world! Fish by the river, sit quietly on a bench, drink at the bar or eat at a table - use these interactive elements to <strong><i>trick your opponents</i></strong> and avoid detection while you track down the target.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815290/extras/0c91e4357c5c12d473c40366a2b83e3f.poster.avif?t=1755349297\" width=614 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815290/extras/0c91e4357c5c12d473c40366a2b83e3f.webm?t=1755349297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1815290/extras/0c91e4357c5c12d473c40366a2b83e3f.mp4?t=1755349297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BODYGUARD</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hitmen unlock clues by interacting with the world to find and kill the target. Bodyguards are here to identify and stop them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HITMAN</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spot the target on the screen and kill it before other players do! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HUNT</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunters need to eliminate the hunted. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEATHMATCH</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eliminate all other players - but don't kill innocent passersby!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DRESS-UP!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the first to wear all the clothes displayed on the target screen by killing the pedestrians that have them! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KILL THEM ALL</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extermination: kill everything that walks! When there are only players left, the round goes into battle royale mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CROWN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wear the crown for longer than other players to win the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PAINT THEM ALL!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team-up! You and your team must paint everyone on the map with your team's color!</p>",
